Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------PREV-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.15,0:00:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗伊·玛斯坦上校的病房在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.51,0:00:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问您的姓名？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫诺克斯 城里的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你传话过去他就知道了
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点来头的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的秘密武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 那小子消沉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦尔地区栽培的农作物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一年种两次的为主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一年种两次 是一年收两次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样怎能得民心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你说是一年收两次什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麦和棉花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且是查过的 很早以前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说当总统之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先解决伊修瓦尔问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就说这要当总统的念头…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是诺克斯医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 看来…你很精神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这群人吵得我不得安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.01,0:01:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说这是真理赐予梦想未来之人的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.88,0:01:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我是不会就此止步不前的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当总统…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你说还要解决伊修瓦尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修瓦尔歼灭战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一切的开端
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你我而言都是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要作个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了结…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先开放伊修瓦尔封锁区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后让各贫民区的伊修瓦尔人回归其圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有许多事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏斯卡和伊修瓦尔人民才能渡过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得报恩才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校 你要的资料拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这不会抵消罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们想从力所能及的事情做起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你们这些人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 马尔科啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来都不用我们开口说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尔科医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛斯坦上校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个能恢复视力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.15,0:03:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这石头是我过去用伊修瓦尔人民的生命炼成的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来说或许有所冒犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若为复兴伊修瓦尔 他们或许会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我无法为他们代言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这是我个人的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能用这块石头来治好你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了伊修瓦尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许他们会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.01,0:03:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有钢仔也会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但请你用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为条件 我将倾尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人比我更需要这块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要排在他之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 80年承蒙厚爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈勃克杂货店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 布莱达 怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 现在马上去中央市？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 什么叫去了就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤势如何 斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是为了获得炼丹术而救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过情况有变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛斯坦那家伙为了伊修瓦尔政策
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我把麦尔兹给他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我想带你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不是作为斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是以一名伊修瓦尔人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 要为复兴伊修瓦拉教而尽力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让历史悠久的宗教和文化消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化之死就是民族之死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的手从死亡中拯救民族吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获救的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让我再活一阵 继续寻找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此身愿随你前往任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.66,0:05:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 麦尔兹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要顺利搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛斯坦那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若知道斯卡还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会大惊失色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯卡 你的真名叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死过两次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是这世上的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无名即可 随意叫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期 伊修瓦尔人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到肌肉退化到这个地步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我背你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用自己的脚来走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我慢慢走回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们是一起离开家的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一阵子没维修了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啦 怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来不知道麟他们回到新国没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都过了两个月了 也该到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅她还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 交给那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 张家的皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 别用那么凶的表情瞪我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在别国蹚这浑水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果连贤者之石也没拿到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下任帝位是姚家的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姚家会负责保护你家门的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是连人造人格利德都接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张家和其他家族 也会统统接受的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那什么脸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:09:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 新国的人是必守盟约的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统统接受真是太贪心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姚麟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.58,0:09:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是传染了那家伙的癖性啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想早点为阿福下葬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 回见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了好多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说阿尔冯斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新国的皇女殿下张梅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很中意你啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是哥哥你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉的事没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴恩 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴恩 好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来啦
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB-----------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不擅长这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 还没修好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到处去打招呼累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉那家伙还拼命使唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉说烤了苹果派 要我们去喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以看得更远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辽阔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我一直在想一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我也在想同一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 问题堆积如山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.74,0:13:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子老了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此 东边有玛斯坦君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北边有阿姆斯特朗君都干得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这老骨头总算也能坐稳总统之位了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让位给后进吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能让给年轻人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得跟去世的布拉德雷一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人也是工作一边倒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是无比的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正经啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 塞利姆 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸟受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮帮它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让爷爷请兽医吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能治好吗 小鸟能治好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长成了个温柔的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定抚养那孩子时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都反对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:15:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他是茁壮成长 一点不用操心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可还得观察一阵子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当那孩子发生异变时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让它发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人和人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能够心灵相通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多老都令人兴奋期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华君有没有为左腿的事消沉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说为了自戒 腿还是保持机械铠的好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他说 没这个温莉会发愁的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？这炫耀帝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能恢复原状真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人也会开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以修兹先生为首
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在许多地方有许多人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给了我们许多…许多的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 这次该我们来回报大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炼金术师所谓的等价交换吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是拿了10就要还10
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到10还要加上自己的1 还11才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然渺小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是我们找到的新的法则
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然需要今后来证明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有什么想做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个女孩我们没能救她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直忘不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰尔索先生 赞帕诺先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多着呢 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳驾 加份牛奶和三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 都打完招呼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 终于该…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去新国
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算去找小梅学习真正的炼丹术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是新国
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要云游东方各国
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握各种各样的学问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见识各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.06,0:17:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解各种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识各种人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你们真的要跟来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟着你们就有好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一直这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们野生的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要寻找恢复身体的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不放弃 这可是你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能靠别人 要自己行动才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥不去新国吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我去东边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥去西边 掌握知识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后两人合东西方的知识
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就能避免重复妮娜那样的不幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.91,0:18:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和哥哥的想法还不止如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想见识见识广阔世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天要上油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.38,0:19:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要检查螺丝的松紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡要擦干水分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样马上就会坏掉不得不回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要整备的时候一定要先打电话预约哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预约…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啦 说清楚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等价交换
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生给你一半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的人生也给我一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 炼金术师为什么都这德性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么等价交换法则 傻不傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说一半了 全部给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…还是不给全部了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9成…不 8成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7不行吧…那8.5？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这点应该可以给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此轻易就颠覆了等价交换法则
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么意思嘛 耍我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有精神了 谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 爱德华君也踏上旅途了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不安分一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.57,0:21:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是宅着不动的男人太无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不伴随痛楚的教训就没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人若无牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会有收获
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而当战胜这痛楚时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.51,0:22:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人就将获得不屈服于任何事物的坚强之心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁般的心
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT-----------------------------------
